  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Independent Data Verification of the Payment by Results Scheme in the Rural Water Sub-Sector in Tanzania</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of the project is to conduct independent data verification for DFID&apos;s Payment by Results scheme in Tanzania&apos;s rural water sub-sector. The results of the independent verification will be used by DFID to determine the level of results-based incentive payment to be disbursed by DFID to Local Government Authorities across Tanzania.</narrative>
  </description>
